  Locus:
    Page: 472
    Verse: 4
Tags:
  - Thoughts
---
If you don’t catch ... thoughts as they rise, they sprout, become plants
and, if you still neglect them, they grow into great trees. ... If you can
be so indifferent to it that it doesn’t sprout or flourish, you are well on
the way to escaping from the entanglements of the mind.
